<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.285216>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Sampling sites of holotype materials and new materials: k, Elaphognathia kikuchii; n, Gnathia nasuta; s, Gnathia sanrikuensis; m, Gnathia mutsuensis; b, Gnathia bungoensis. The numbers correspond to the specimen numbers in Table 1." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/285216/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.285217>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Elaphognathia kikuchii (Nunomura, 1992) (KMNH IvR- 500,705) collected off the Koshiki Islands: A, body, dorsal view; B, cephalosome, dorsal view; C, cephalosome, dorsolateral view; D, cephalosome, lateral view; E, pleotelson, dorsal view; F, right antennule; G, right antenna." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/285217/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.285218>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Elaphognathia kikuchii (Nunomura, 1992) (KMNH IvR- 500,705) collected off the Koshiki Islands: A, right maxilliped, ventral view; B right pylopod, ventral view; C, right pereopod II, lateral view; D, right pleopod II; E, penes." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/285218/files/figure.png" ;
